00:00:27.390 --> 00:00:32.870
It's. Today we have here Dr.
Paul Evans Holbrook to speak

00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:35.950
to us about the victor
[inaudible] collection

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:39.150
and there is perhaps no
one more knowledgeable

00:00:39.150 --> 00:00:46.490
about victor [inaudible] than
Mr. Holbrook, Dr. Holbrook.

00:00:46.490 --> 00:00:49.530
He became close friends
with Caroline about 2 years

00:00:49.530 --> 00:00:55.080
after victor passed away
and he was instrumental

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.390
in getting the victor
[inaudible] collection,

00:00:57.390 --> 00:01:00.510
victor and Caroline
[inaudible] collection here

00:01:00.510 --> 00:01:03.530
to the library of congress.

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:08.230
This all started about, well at
least for us here, our interest

00:01:08.230 --> 00:01:13.070
