01:05:08.150 --> 01:05:09.450
&gt;&gt; DR. PAUL EVANS HOLBROOK:
Doesn't seem as long,

01:05:09.450 --> 01:05:11.740
but at any rate, came back
and helped make it get the,

01:05:11.740 --> 01:05:14.480
get things filed away which we.

01:05:14.480 --> 01:05:17.310
I came on Wednesday
and left on Saturday

01:05:17.310 --> 01:05:23.740
